title: AUD/USD Holding First Resistance At 6875/85 Targets 6860
text:
AUD/USD NZD/USD Daily Chart

holding first resistance at 6875/85 targets 6860 with first support at 6849/45. Better support at 6830/25 could hold the downside but longs need stops below 6815. Shorts at resistance at 6875/85 need stops above 6895. A break higher targets 6910 and 6930/40.

first resistance at 6430/35 but above 6445 targets a selling opportunity at 6460/70. Stop above 6480. A break higher is a buy signal targeting 6500 and 6520/30. Minor support at 6405/00 then a buying opportunity at 6380/70, with stops below 6355. A break lower targets 6335/30, perhaps as far as 6305/00.
